text: Model 67 may refer to: * Curtiss BF2C Goshawk (Model 67), a United States naval biplane aircraft in the 1930s * IBM System/360 Model 67, an IBM mainframe computer of the late 1960s * Model 67 mine, an Austrian anti-tank mine * Mauser-Norris Model 67, a German bolt-action rifle * Smith & Wesson Model 67, an American revolver * Winchester Model 67, an American bolt-action rifle
title: Model 67
